text: Alba Cañabate Pinheiro (born 21 July 1999) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Andorra women's national team. ==Career== Cañabate has been capped for the Andorra national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers Category:Andorran people of Spanish descent Category:Andorran people of Portuguese descent
